          "_name": "features015",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features15\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\" checked>\n\t\t<header>Card</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showCardTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Images\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n\t\t<select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n\t\t\t<option value=\"12\">1</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"6\">2</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"4\" selected>3</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"3\">4</option>\n\t\t</select>\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#000000\" selected>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t<header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\n\t<div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n\t</div>\n\t<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mbr-section-head mb-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Calibrated</b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">These pieces made it through setup and stayed on their marks. The signal held. The point survived. These are the thoughts that behaved long enough to be recorded on purpose.</h5>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}} active\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"slim-shady.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-3-192x128.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b><a href=\"slim-shady.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Slim Shady</a></b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"inter-small-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>A reflection on mortality, matter, and the uncomfortable fact that we are all just temporary arrangements pretending to be permanent.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"the-present-ledger.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-5-192x128.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b><a href=\"the-present-ledger.html\" class=\"text-primary\">The Present Leger</a></b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"inter-small-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">A reckoning with how life gets spent, what gets wasted, and what still counts.</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"markerless-thoughts.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-6-192x128.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b><a href=\"markerless-thoughts.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Markerless Thoughts</a></b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"inter-small-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">A piece about tribalism, conspiracies, and the human habit of locking onto certainty without enough evidence.</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"give-it-to-me.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-192x122.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-bs-slide-to=\"3\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b><a href=\"give-it-to-me.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Give it to me!</a></b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"inter-small-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">A thought piece about gifts, gratitude, and the strange difference between wanting things and being known.</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"how-you-doin.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-192x123.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"4\" data-bs-slide-to=\"4\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b><a href=\"how-you-doin.html\" class=\"text-primary\">How You doin'?</a></b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"inter-small-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">A piece about wealth, happiness, and the kind of wisdom that sounds simple until life proves otherwise.</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"flat-chemtrails.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-192x192.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"5\" data-bs-slide-to=\"5\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b><a href=\"flat-chemtrails.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Flat Chemtrails</a></b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"inter-small-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">A satirical signal about belief, absurdity, and the blurry line between paranoia and pattern-seeking.</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"retro-reflections.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-4-192x128.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-bs-slide-to=\"6\" data-slide-to=\"6\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b><a href=\"retro-reflections.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Retro Reflections</a></b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"inter-small-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">A look backward at love, loss, time, and what remains after the noise settles.</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"tracking-what-matters.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-7-192x128.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-bs-slide-to=\"7\" data-slide-to=\"7\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b><a href=\"tracking-what-matters.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Tracking What Matters</a></b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"inter-small-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">A more deliberate reflection on what deserves attention, memory, and emotional bandwidth.</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"the-maiden-name.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-2-192x128.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-bs-slide-to=\"8\" data-slide-to=\"8\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b><a href=\"the-maiden-name.html\" class=\"text-primary\">The Maiden Name</a></b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"inter-small-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA ray of light in the snow.</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
